                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010520-26-off144 t18010520-26-cd145"></join>, a copper tea-kettle, value 20s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010520-26-victim222" type="victimName">
                     Samuel 
                     Hawkes
                  <interp inst="t18010520-26-victim222" type="surname" value="Hawkes"></interp>
